   - deraadt@cvs.openbsd.org 2000/08/18 20:07:23
     [ssh.c]
     accept remsh as a valid name as well; roman@buildpoint.com
   - deraadt@cvs.openbsd.org 2000/08/18 20:17:13
     [deattack.c crc32.c packet.c]
